data.description: Here is a large detached home close to schools and recreation.  Unique floor plan gives privacy space and family togetherness. The first floor consists of a  living room which flows nicely into the dining room.  The kitchen is in the back of the home. There is a very large walk-in pantry off dining room. There is also a 1/2 bath right off the kitchen & 1st floor laundry.  Updated kitchen and all appliances go with it. Dishwasher, stove, refrigerator, washer and dryer.  At the top of the stairs is another room which could be a walk through bedroom if needed or a playroom, computer or game room.  Large Primary bedroom with a huge walk in closet for all of your clothes in in the back of the home.  Could be changed into a en-suite bathroom. The other two bedrooms  have laminate flooring and ample closet space.  Most windows are replacement windows.  Fenced in yard leading to a 2 car garage with electric door openers, . Patio off the kitchen is great for outside entertainment
